CustomField.description: This is used to set the name of a Custom Batch class that will run after each Summary Batch. The custom batch class should implement the ScheduledDispatcher.IScheduledDispatcher interface.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This is used to set the name of a Custom Batch class that will run after each Summary Batch. The custom batch class should implement the ScheduledDispatcher.IScheduledDispatcher interface.
CustomField.label: Custom Batch Name
